1. *Duše* su se sastali u večnoj ljubavi. (Souls met in eternal love.)

2. Ona je od *duše* želela da uspe na ispitu. (She earnestly wanted to pass her exam.)

3. Ona je volela da uživa u duševnim blagodetima. (She liked to indulge in spiritual blessings.)

4. Ona je uživala u *duši* njegove ljubavi. (She enjoyed the soul of his love.)

5. U njegovim očima mogla se videti *duša*. (In his eyes one could see the soul.)

6. Ona je mogla da utiče na *duše* ljudi. (She was able to touch the souls of people.)